Raisi also traveled Aytollah Al-Hashem, Imam of Juma Tabriz, Foreign Minister Hossein Amirabdollahian, Governor of Azerbaijan Oriental Malik Rahmati and many others, reports the information body. The difficult weather conditions, the rain, the thick fog and the arrival of the dark are complicating the work of rescue teams even if, as reportedly &nbsp;vice President Mohsen Mansouri, quoted by Irna (the printing agency of the Islamic Republic), rescuers would establish a contact > with at least two passengers.&nbsp;Raisi was back from the opening of a dam on Iran.
